      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi James,\n\nI just thought I'd mention...\nThe requestlock (formerly lockahead) patch adds a little bit of ladvise sanity checking (since I wanted it for my code): https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/13564/\n\nJust thought that might be interesting to you.\n\nAlso, I'd be happy to review this patch once it's ready.  (Right now it's not passing its own test.  Is that because it found bugs?)",
